abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bennett, Robb, Copley, Claudia, Copley, Darren (2023): Revision of the western Nearctic spider genus Cybaeina including the description of Neocybaeina gen. nov. and Rothaeina gen. nov.
